data.description: USDA 0% Down Eligible Location! Welcome to this beautifully maintained home located in the heart of Deer Park! With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, there's plenty of space to live and grow comfortably. The open living and dining areas have abundant natural light, making this home feel inviting and spacious.  The elegant kitchen is a dream with its stainless steel appliances, granite counters, added island space, and bright soft-close cabinetry-creating a hub for gatherings. An attached two-car garage offers convenience and extra storage space for all your needs. Main-floor laundry room with an outside entry makes a great mudroom. The spacious backyard is perfectly landscaped for outdoor activities and relaxing evenings. It is centrally located, offering easy access to schools and parks.
